title: American horror story asylum - sister Eunice traps sister Jude with the murderous Santa

comment: Man, I remember when American Horror Story used to be good like this. What happened?
I don't know why this scene is so terrifying to me!
This was done incredibly! The acting, the editing and on top of all Carol Of The Bells 😍🙌
I do feel bad for Sister Jude but this scene is darkly funny
